S-01 High
Secure login to the portal
As a loan applicant, I want to log in securely using my credentials so that only I can access my application and personal data.
Acceptance criteria
User can log in with email + password or OTP via mobile number
Failed login after 3 attempts locks the account for 15 minutes
Session expires after 30 minutes of inactivity
JWT token is issued on successful authentication

US-02 High
Multi-factor authentication
As a loan applicant, I want to verify my identity with a second factor so that my account is protected even if my password is compromised.
Acceptance criteria
OTP sent via SMS or email within 30 seconds
OTP expires after 5 minutes
User is notified of new login attempts from unrecognised devices

US-03 High
Submit identity documents
As a loan applicant, I want to upload my government-issued ID so that the system can verify my identity before processing my application.
Acceptance criteria
Supports passport, national ID, and driver's licence uploads
Accepted formats: JPG, PNG, PDF — max 5 MB per file
Uploaded documents are scanned for tampering or forgery
User receives confirmation when documents are successfully received

US-04 High
Automated KYC decision
As a compliance officer, I want KYC checks to run automatically via third-party APIs so that we can process applications faster without manual review for straightforward cases.
Acceptance criteria
KYC API returns a pass/fail decision within 60 seconds
On failure, the application is terminated and the applicant is notified
All KYC API responses are logged with timestamps for audit
Edge cases flagged for manual review rather than auto-rejection
